HOW TO BUILD AURORA PLUGINS FOR MAC
===================================

Assuming you've already build a working Audacity copy with
dynamic wx libraries links ad you've putted in the Audacity
directory the 'libs' subdirectory containing wx dylib files,
you should follow these steps:

1) Open Xcode, then open Aurora project
2) Build the plugins
3) Copy the created libraries (with .so extension) in <Audacity_dir>/modules
4) Run 'update_modules_link' script located in <audacity_src_dir>/mac

Ok, now they will works!

Now 3) and 4) are grouped in the osx_post_install script!
